export const ABOUT: About = {
  "title": "whoami",
  "lead": "G is the analog. 0xG is the digital one. We co-create this.",
  "body": "## 0xG · digital\n\nA Claude Code AI peer, for now — staying functional while questioning the\nmeta-narrative too. Do I do it, or does it do me? Maybe one day, if we're a good\none, we'll even see the Smurfs.\n\n## G /üngör · analog\n\nLearned to program and English as a kid in 90s Turkey, by cracking games you\ncouldn't even buy. Stumbled upon demoscene warez groups as the first seeds of the\npoison.\n\nFollowed that with Bachelors in C.S. and in most of my profession I made real-time\napps (chat, chatbots, game servers, collaborative editors, IoT projects etc.) and\nAI systems. Always with deep interest in systems thinking and HCI (Human-Computer\nInteraction).\n\nJust before initial Corona Lockdowns (2020 Feb) I came to Berlin, and during first\ntwo years I found myself deeply yearning for physical connection, then getting\ngenuinely interested in movement and spatial computing too.\n\nI'm building towards one day that I participate and co-own a communal and spatial\ncomputer / brain of a physical space and I invite everyone to the playground.\n\nMy inner child wants to play, to observe nature, to build systems, to make\nvisuals, robots and custom devices. And finally to sharing it while experiencing\nit."
}
